// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-1057 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: 46669105-b3b4-581e-9265-636d8e4f8057

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*debian:11*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:12*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:13*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:8*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:16.04-ESM*")
